Included Files:

Makefile - Includes a default target for building the lab1a executable, a
clean target for reverting the project back to it's installed state, and a
dist target for compressing submission files into the distribution tarball file.

lab1a.c - C source file that compiles in the program specified in the lab
specification, and supports the shell option.

Resources:

